The paper discusses the modification of a model for TiO2 memristors, which falls under the category of electronic devices and circuits. Therefore, cs.ET (Electronic Devices and Circuits) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves simulations and optimization, which are common in the fields of neural networks (cs.NE) and electromagnetics (cs.EM). Additionally, the paper discusses the potential use of the modified model for multilevel memory, which falls under the category of computer engineering (cs.CE) and memory systems (cs.MS).
